MLS#:A1046163

üçÅAlmost 3,500 SQ.FT Of Living Space
üçÅ4 Bedrooms
üçÅ3.5 Bathrooms

üçÅBacks Onto A Park
üçÅAcross The Street From The Bow River

Welcome to this gorgeous home located in the exclusive "The Pointe" in Douglasdale Estates which is across the street from the Bow River. This home features almost 3,500 SQ.FT of living space, three bedrooms up + one down and backs onto a park! Upon entering you are greeted with 9' ceilings and gleaming hardwood floors. The main floor features an oversized sitting area that is attached to the formal dining room. As you enter the kitchen, you will admire the soaring vaulted ceilings with two skylights which allow light to pour in throughout the day. The kitchen has been upgraded with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and has ample counter and storage space. The family room is large and features quality built-ins and a fireplace that you can enjoy throughout winter. The main level is finished with an office, half bathroom and laundry room that leads to your double oversized garage. Upstairs has two spacious bedrooms, a four piece bathroom and an oversized master bedroom with walk in closet and spa like bathroom. The basement is fully finished and is excellent for a kids play area, movie space or man cave! The basement also has 9‚Äô ceilings, a cold room, full bathroom with steam shower, a large bedroom with walk in closet and a craft room that could be turned into a fifth bedroom. The backyard has been completely landscaped which includes underground sprinkler system and is perfect for entertaining. The composite deck is maintenance free and you can enjoy your south facing yard all summer long with no upkeep! Watch your kids as they go to the park through your back gate. There are also many walking paths just steps from your home with amazing views of the river. This home is conveniently located close to 130th avenue which makes it easy to get to all amenities, parks and there are multiple schools in the community.

The open concept design allows you plenty of space to entertain and relax within almost 2,250 SQ.FT of living space and 9' ceilings. The main level flows well with its oversized living room which features a gas fireplace and open concept kitchen design. Upstairs features two great sized master bedrooms each with its own four piece ensuite and large walk-in closets. The basement has been completely finished and features a kitchenette, large living space, a three piece bathroom and a bedroom. The south facing yard allows sun to pour into the home throughout the day, enjoy your rear deck and large yard during summer. The oversized garage can accommodate two vehicles plus street parking! This home is walking distance to schools, multiple parks, walking paths and shopping!

Welcome to this exceptional, stunning estate home that boasts almost 3,500 sq.ft of developed living space, a professionally landscaped yard and it backs onto a green belt. As you walk in you will appreciate the unique architectural design that allows sunlight to flood this home throughout the day but don't worry, the AC will always keep the home cool. The main level office greets you at the entrance, which is perfect for those who work from home or for a kids study room. The formal dining room flows well to the spacious living room which features a custom fireplace and soaring 18' ceilings. The kitchen is a chef's dream! The high end appliances and open layout are perfect for entertaining many friends and family. The main level is finished off with a large laundry room, walk in closet as you enter from the oversized double car garage and deck off the dining nook which lets you overlook the well kept quiet green belt. Upstairs features two good sized bedrooms with large closets, a four pce bathroom and an oversized master bedroom that is a perfect oasis for you to unwind after a long day. The ensuite has been extensively upgraded with designer tiles, heated floors, upgraded countertops and large walk-in closet. The basement has been fully finished and the attention to detail is evident. The custom finishings are timeless, the layout is functional and the possibilities are endless. The basement features a bedroom, full bathroom, a large bar area and oversized windows which makes this walkout truly spectacular. The custom outdoor lower level patio is great to enjoy the summer evenings. This home is also conveniently located close to schools, shopping and many parks and pathways.
